title: Destiny Land
description: Woo-geon, a fan of amusement park, ended up working at Destiny Land as if guided by fate. However, it was the start of his misery when he was constantly being ignored and bullied every day by his childhood nemesis, Choyi. Then one day, by chance, Woo-geon gets hold of a mysterious tarot card and gains the ability to control women, leading to a drastic change in his life...
author: Dongsakdong Red Keyboard
